{"tid":2291010,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"其實應唔應該send cv去啲獵頭公司或者招聘代理公司","createTime":"2020-11-18T12:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-19T06:07:57.000Z","uid":189356,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"629e508aec251bac67d469cd5615d231e2c610ef","tid":2291010,"uid":189356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:24:28.000Z","msg":"因為過去揾工都係自己去揾，所以未試過靠獵頭公司，但最近係求職網站見到有獵頭公司出左個招聘廣告，個職位都岩自己心水，但驚間獵頭公司唔可靠，又怕個啲agent拎左自己個人資料用係其他用途，始終cv有齊自己地址，啲reference letter又有身份證號碼"},{"pid":"cd27cd7b5175947a2756b27790160f368e57fa77","tid":2291010,"uid":9260,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"就算直接send cv<br />\n都從來唔寫自己身分證號碼同詳細地址<br />\n最多寫自己住邊區<br />\n咪一樣搵到工份份都上市公司<br />\n你寫係你戇鳩姐"},{"pid":"44e1434bac669d448adc47955e736f49e3ac757d","tid":2291010,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"CV寫full address<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又咁快俾reference letter<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc9835143b101589d64678bc13fe886f9a12ce9","tid":2291010,"uid":298442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e1434bac669d448adc47955e736f49e3ac757d","tid":2291010,"uid":196924,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:32:52.000Z","msg":"CV寫full address<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又咁快俾reference letter<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:41:58.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講以為係application form"},{"pid":"951d043268da4acb9a8f0572005ef38c75ab7536","tid":2291010,"uid":73026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-18T12:58:58.000Z","msg":"CV 寫地址<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f62d345bf9dec6d2810c252e323f58841057834","tid":2291010,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T00:41:48.000Z","msg":"驚咪只留電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n傾完啱傾先俾email囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c71ee31760bbe98f5ad22dee622f4bb10b1927e","tid":2291010,"uid":361975,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T01:24:48.000Z","msg":"初初畢業因為自己唔想搵工所以會<br />\n到自己再大個啲夠cv會慢慢認真揀公司睇福利，唔會再搵中介"},{"pid":"30b1ab893add6f2a840f72ca12bcc5681da5e778","tid":2291010,"uid":35206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T06:07:57.000Z","msg":"有headhunt叫我俾CV佢，話有工介紹<br />\n我俾左（得電話同email），但佢收到之後唔再理我<br />\n<br />\n之後見到佢post左份工，話有興趣send email俾佢<br />\n我Send左俾佢，又係冇下文<br />\n之後成日有銀行打嚟問我借唔借錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}